defaultmber of documentaries or campaign-focused programmes as set out in the remit. 
default&#xa0;
default•
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe Radio1 schedule duplicates content already available on commercial radio. It features popular celebrities and events that are widely covered on commercial radio,
default therefore it is not distinctive or catering for underserved audiences. 
