defaultIt should offer entertaining popular music pro
defaultgrammes and speech-based content including news, current affairs, documentaries, religion, arts, comedy, readings and social action output.”
default&#xa0;
defaultIf Radio2 were a new publicly funded service this format would not be approved for launch because this remit is va
defaultgue and does not place an emphasis on public service content. It emulates much of what is available on commercial stations. Its remit to appeal to a ‘broad audience’ is counterproductive for a public service broadcaster because the focus should be on under
defaultserved audiences and content not provided elsewhere.  
